<h1 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.2;">Welcome aboard!</h1>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Our team just finished creating your TechFlash account for <strong><%= @user.email %></strong>.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">Click the button below to get started. You&rsquo;ll set a secure password (at least 6 characters, with uppercase, lowercase, a number, and a special character). This link expires in 72 hours.</p>
<% if @membership_context.present? %>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
    Your account is on the <strong><%= @membership_context[:tier_name] %></strong> tier with a platform commission of <strong><%= @membership_context[:commission_display] %></strong>
    and monthly membership fee of <strong><%= @membership_context[:monthly_fee_display] %></strong>.
  </p>
<% end %>
<% if @user.company? %>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">After you sign in, you&rsquo;ll land on your dashboard where you can post a job and hire technicians.</p>
<% elsif @user.technician? %>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">After you sign in, browse open jobs and claim work that fits your skills.</p>
<% end %>

<%= render partial: 'user_mailer/cta_button', locals: { text: 'Log in & set password', url: @reset_url } %>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5;">If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br/><span style="word-break: break-all;"><%= @reset_url %></span></p>
